# CODEOWNERS
# GeniegoROI Repository Code Ownership
# CCIS Part002 — Repository & Monorepo Architecture
# Version 1.0 | 2026-07-22
#
# 형식: {패턴} {GitHub 유저명 또는 팀}
# 패턴 순서: 마지막 매칭 규칙이 우선 적용됨
#
# NOTE: GitHub 유저명이 설정되지 않은 경우 아래 항목들을 실제 계정으로 교체하십시오.
# 예: @genieroi/frontend-team, @genieroi/backend-team

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Default Owner (전체 Repository 기본 소유자)
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
*                           @genieroi/core-team

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Frontend Module
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
frontend/                   @genieroi/frontend-team
frontend/src/               @genieroi/frontend-team
frontend/android/           @genieroi/mobile-team
frontend/ios/               @genieroi/mobile-team
frontend/scripts/           @genieroi/frontend-team
frontend/package.json       @genieroi/frontend-team
frontend/vite.config.js     @genieroi/frontend-team
frontend/capacitor.config.json  @genieroi/mobile-team

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Backend Module
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
backend/                    @genieroi/backend-team
backend/src/                @genieroi/backend-team
backend/migrations/         @genieroi/backend-team @genieroi/dba
backend/composer.json       @genieroi/backend-team

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Infrastructure & Deployment
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
infra/                      @genieroi/devops-team
infra/aws/                  @genieroi/devops-team
infra/azure/                @genieroi/devops-team
docker-compose.yml          @genieroi/devops-team
.github/                    @genieroi/devops-team
.github/workflows/          @genieroi/devops-team

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Security-sensitive files (반드시 Security Team Review 필요)
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
.githooks/                  @genieroi/security-team
.github/workflows/security-scan.yml  @genieroi/security-team
backend/src/SecurityAudit.php        @genieroi/security-team
backend/src/Crypto.php               @genieroi/security-team
backend/src/Ssrf.php                 @genieroi/security-team

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Configuration & Repository Governance
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
.gitignore                  @genieroi/core-team
.gitattributes              @genieroi/core-team
.editorconfig               @genieroi/core-team
CODEOWNERS                  @genieroi/core-team
Makefile                    @genieroi/core-team
scripts/validation/         @genieroi/core-team

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Documentation
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
docs/                       @genieroi/architecture-team
docs/ccis/                  @genieroi/architecture-team
docs/architecture/          @genieroi/architecture-team
